## 1. Form Creation and Layout
- Test all form element drag-and-drop functionality
- Verify responsive design across different screen sizes
- Check form element alignment and spacing
- Validate form template functionality

## 2. Input Field Validation
- Test all input field types (text, number, email, etc.)
- Verify custom validation rules
- Check error message display and formatting
- Test field masking and formatting

## 3. Form Submission Flows
- Test multi-step form navigation
- Verify form submission with large datasets
- Check success/error handling
- Test partial save functionality

## 4. Conditional Logic
- Test if/then rules for form fields
- Verify complex nested conditions
- Check condition-based field visibility
- Test conditional validation rules

## 5. File Upload Features
- Test multiple file upload functionality
- Verify file size limitations
- Check supported file type restrictions
- Test upload progress indicators

## 6. Form Analytics
- Verify completion rate tracking
- Test user interaction analytics
- Check form abandonment tracking
- Validate analytics dashboard accuracy

## 7. Integration Testing
- Test API connections
- Verify third-party service integrations
- Check database synchronization
- Test webhook functionality

## 8. Performance Testing
- Test form load times
- Verify concurrent user handling
- Check server response times
- Test form caching mechanisms

## 9. Accessibility Compliance
- Test screen reader compatibility
- Verify keyboard navigation
- Check WCAG 2.1 compliance
- Test high-contrast mode

## 10. Security Testing
- Test input sanitization
- Verify CSRF protection
- Check form encryption
- Test rate limiting functionality
